profile:
Budget Blinds of Medicine Hat and The Foothills proudly serves residential and commercial customers in the following areas: Medicine Hat, Redcliff, Brooks, Rosemary, Duchess, Bassano, Lyalta, Strathmore, Langdon, Okotoks, Black Diamond, High River, Dewinton, Turner Valley, Bragg Creek, Canmore, Banff, Claresholm, Drumheller, Oyen, Acadia Valley, Hanna. We are a window covering franchise, offering custom, high quality and stylish window coverings for any occasion including blinds, shades, shutters, and drapes. Regardless of your window's unique shape or size, we have a window covering solution for you. We’ll bring samples, swatches and styles to you so you can see how they look in your home! We do it all for you - design, measure and install, and back it up with the best warranty in the business. Request your free in-home or virtual consultation today!

Budget Blinds offers:
• Convenient at-home service
• Professional installation
• Free consultations and estimates
• Knowledgeable consultants
• Expert measuring
• Quality, name-brand window treatments
• Excellent Warranty

Visit us at budgetblinds.com/medicinehat to learn more about our special offers and how Budget Blinds can help create your dream home environment!
